featured_reviews.review_id:
This is sunni Jama masjid. It is nearly 40 years old, located a little inside from the main road, but still it is very useful.
It has a tall minar which can be seen from far. At the time of last Ramadan air-coolers were installed at ground floor. All basic amenities are available. But toilets are insufficient. Progress is too slow.
